{"tid":95653,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【三點九沈大師】大師：今日唔好做嘢住 2017-1-26","createTime":"2017-01-26T07:55:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T16:08:41.000Z","uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0f276d7833d11cb86ec4776b8ea181b258944d7c","tid":95653,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T07:55:56.000Z","msg":"【三點九沈大師】大師：今日唔好做嘢住<br />\n2017-1-26 15:40:56<br />\n<br />\n【三點九沈大師】大師：今日唔好做嘢住 <br />\n<br />\n又到《三點九沈大師》時間，個市衝到上去23400嘅位暫時停一停，我估計聽日個市都係牛牛皮皮嘅，暫時策略就唔好郁手住，再高追都意義不大，預佢放完假返o黎個交易日有機會「紅盤高開」，不過未必太驚喜嘅啫，往後個市仍然都會係反覆，所以今日唔好做嘢住，聽日我嘗試喺11:45或11:00左右畀一個指示大家，睇下聽日半日市我哋有咩部署喇。"},{"pid":"61e4246bca60a1dfc4e1330e67686d8e6228864a","tid":95653,"uid":65140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T07:57:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/91231b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F91231b.jpg&h=c9f42e52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/981125.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F981125.jpg&h=af2464e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/929c7e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F929c7e.jpg&h=5d808d3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/5aba31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F5aba31.jpg&h=5f359a57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/2e8691.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F2e8691.jpg&h=75b7357f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/944bb2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F944bb2.jpg&h=f1cdf002&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/29be46.jpg\" data-thumbn