kgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有河圖，有洛書，<br />\n之後先有周文王的周易易經。<br />\n<br />\n有師父的神諭天機<br />\n先有樣子兄的阻力圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12a292989c26db55459590f068d92476ac55c2e3","tid":95653,"uid":29928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T14:12:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>【三點九沈大師】大師：今日唔好做嘢住<br />\n2017-1-26 15:40:56<br />\n<br />\n【三點九沈大師】大師：今日唔好做嘢住 <br />\n<br />\n又到《三點九沈大師》時間，個市衝到上去23400嘅位暫時停一停，我估計<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">聽日</span></span>個市都係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">牛牛</span></span>皮皮嘅，暫時策略就唔好郁手住，再高追都意義不大，預佢放完假返o黎個交易日有機會「<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">紅盤高開</span></span>」，不過<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">未必太驚喜</span></span>嘅啫，往後個市仍然都會係反覆，所以今日唔好做嘢住，聽日我嘗試喺11:45或11:00左右畀一個指示大家，睇下聽日半日市我哋有咩部署喇。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 信息量巨大"},{"pid":"d81b955d60c5f48864ea0dcf121c30b2b1314ffa","tid":95653,"uid":33907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T14:13:36.000Z","msg":"多謝大師<br />\n23390-1<br />\n23295平左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd717c12dcf04df07dc7e2ca3ca59d2106890f8b","tid":95653,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T14:33:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多謝大師<br />\n23390-1<br />\n23295平左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n師父：四海之內皆兄弟.jpg <br />\n師父：最緊要請食飯同叫雞.jpg"},{"pid":"187da05a1873c8d67551ca64b8dac71f06a51b84","tid":95653,"uid":45178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T14:42:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>多謝大師<br />\n23390-1<br />\n23295平左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n師父：四海之內皆兄弟.jpg <br />\n師父：最緊要請食飯同叫雞.jpg</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n師父 ：夠未？唔夠話我聽.jpg"},{"pid":"37537a7d5b6